  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git分支管理流程图，展示main、stage、develop-a和develop-b这几个分支的协作关系。先在main上做两个初始提交，然后分出stage作为预发布分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "stage",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，stage从第二个commit分出来。那develop-a和develop-b这两个开发分支是从哪里切出来的？也是从第二个commit同时切，还是先后切？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop-a",
        "develop-b",
        "branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop-a和develop-b都从第二个commit切，三个分支并行。develop-b先往前走两个提交，然后develop-a再开始工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop-a",
        "develop-b",
        "commit",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，develop-b切出来后提交两次，然后checkout到develop-a做两次提交。接下来develop-a要合并到stage吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop-a",
        "develop-b",
        "stage",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，develop-a先合并进stage。然后develop-b也合并进stage。之后develop-a需要再从main同步更新，因为main会合并stage。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop-a",
        "develop-b",
        "stage",
        "main",
        "merge",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我理一下顺序：develop-a合并到stage，develop-b合并到stage，然后checkout main合并stage，接着develop-a和develop-b分别再merge main来同步。是这样吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "stage",
        "develop-a",
        "develop-b",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。同步完之后，develop-b再做两个提交，然后develop-a继续开发，也做两个提交。这样整个流程就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop-a",
        "develop-b",
        "commit",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。我检查下：main两个初始commit，分出stage、develop-a、develop-b，develop-b先走两步，develop-a再走两步并先合入stage，develop-b再合入stage，main合并stage后，develop-a和develop-b分别同步main，最后develop-b两步提交、develop-a两步提交。结构符合你的要求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
